context Movie::stars
derive: self.isRated->iterate(s; v : Int = 0 | v + stars)
context Movie::ratings
derive: self.isRated->size()
context Movie::getRating() : Real
pre: -- none
post: (ratings = 0 and result = 0) or result = stars / ratings
context Movie::duration
derive: self.scenes->iterate(s; v : Int = 0 | v + duration)
context Movie::description : String
init: "Someone should give a brief description of the plot"
context Movie
inv: scenes->forAll(contains->forAll(
c | self.actors->exists(plays->exists(c2 | c2 = c)))
context Rating
inv: user.rated->select(movie = self.movie)->size() = 1
context User::getRated(s : Int) : Set(Movie)
inv: rated->select(stars = s)->collect(movie)
